var mapInstance = $data.component; \r\n
                                        var dataSource = $data.model.listViewDataSource(); \r\n                                        

                                        var appendMarkers = function() { \r\n
                                            var markers = []; \r\n
                                            var originalMarkers = dataSource.items(); \r\n

                                            for (var currentMarkerIndex = 0; currentMarkerIndex < originalMarkers.length; currentMarkerIndex++) { \r\n
                                                (function (currentMarkerIndex) {\r\n
                                                    var originalMarker = originalMarkers[currentMarkerIndex]; \r\n

                                                    var skipCurrentMarker = false; \r\n
                                                    if($model._FullTextSearchInputValue) { \r\n
                                                        var lowerCaseTitle = originalMarker.Title.toLowerCase(); \r\n
                                                        var lowerCaseSearchString = $model._FullTextSearchInputValue.toLowerCase(); \r\n

                                                        if(!lowerCaseTitle.startsWith(lowerCaseSearchString)) \r\n
                                                            skipCurrentMarker = true; \r\n
                                                    } \r\n

                                                    if(!skipCurrentMarker) {
                                                        var latlng = [originalMarker.Latitude, originalMarker.Longitude]; \r\n

                                                        var marker = { \r\n
                                                            location: latlng, \r\n
                                                            title: originalMarker.Title \r\n
                                                        }; \r\n

                                                        if($data.model.encodeHtml) { \r\n
                                                            marker.title = DevExpress.ExpressApp.Mobile.encodeHtml(marker.title); \r\n
                                                        } \r\n

                                                        marker.onClick = function() { \r\n
                                                            var markerClickFunction = eval($data.model.markerClickFunction); \r\n                                                            
                                                            markerClickFunction(originalMarker); \r\n
                                                        }; \r\n
                                                        
                                                        var customMarkerProcessingFunctionString = $data.model.customMarkerProcessingFunction; \r\n
                                                        if(customMarkerProcessingFunctionString != undefined) { \r\n
                                                            var customMarkerProcessingFunction = eval(customMarkerProcessingFunctionString); \r\n
                                                            customMarkerProcessingFunction(mapInstance, marker, originalMarker); \r\n
                                                        } \r\n

                                                        markers.push.apply(markers, [marker]); \r\n
                                                    }
                                                })(currentMarkerIndex); \r\n                                                
                                            } \r\n

                                            mapInstance.option("markers", markers); \r\n

                                            var routesData = $data.model.routesData; \r\n
                                            if(routesData) { \r\n
                                                var useDefaultRoute = routesData.length === 1 && routesData[0].locations === undefined; \r\n
                                                if(useDefaultRoute) { \r\n
                                                    var routes = [];
                                                    if(markers.length > 1) { \r\n
                                                        var defaultRoute = $.extend({}, routesData[0]); \r\n
                                                        var locations = []; \r\n
                                                        for (var currentMarkerIndex = 0; currentMarkerIndex < markers.length; currentMarkerIndex++) { \r\n
                                                            var currentMarkerLocation = markers[currentMarkerIndex].location; \r\n
                                                            locations.push.apply(locations, [currentMarkerLocation]); \r\n
                                                        } \r\n
                                                        defaultRoute.locations = locations; \r\n
                                                        routes = [defaultRoute]; \r\n
                                                    }
                                                    mapInstance.option("routes", routes); \r\n
                                                } else { \r\n
                                                    mapInstance.option("routes", routesData); \r\n
                                                }
                                            } \r\n
                                            var customProcessDataSourceFunctionString = $data.model.customProcessDatasourceFunction; \r\n
                                            if(customProcessDataSourceFunctionString != undefined) { \r\n
                                                var customProcessDataSourceFunction = eval(customProcessDataSourceFunctionString); \r\n
                                                customProcessDataSourceFunction(mapInstance, originalMarkers); \r\n
                                            } \r\n
                                        }; \r\n
                                        dataSource.load().done(function(){ appendMarkers(); }); \r\n
                                        dataSource.on("changed", (function(){ appendMarkers(); })); \r\n
                                        
                                        var customInitializeFunctionString = $data.model.customInitializeFunction; \r\n
                                        if(customInitializeFunctionString != undefined) { \r\n
                                            var customInitializeFunction = eval(customInitializeFunctionString); \r\n
                                            customInitializeFunction(mapInstance); \r\n

var mapInstance = $data.component; \r\n
                                        var dataSource = $data.model.listViewDataSource(); \r\n                                        

                                        var appendMarkers = function() { \r\n
                                            var markers = []; \r\n
                                            var originalMarkers = dataSource.items(); \r\n

                                            for (var currentMarkerIndex = 0; currentMarkerIndex < originalMarkers.length; currentMarkerIndex++) { \r\n
                                                (function (currentMarkerIndex) {\r\n
                                                    var originalMarker = originalMarkers[currentMarkerIndex]; \r\n

                                                    var skipCurrentMarker = false; \r\n
                                                    if($model._FullTextSearchInputValue) { \r\n
                                                        var lowerCaseTitle = originalMarker.Title.toLowerCase(); \r\n
                                                        var lowerCaseSearchString = $model._FullTextSearchInputValue.toLowerCase(); \r\n

                                                        if(!lowerCaseTitle.startsWith(lowerCaseSearchString)) \r\n
                                                            skipCurrentMarker = true; \r\n
                                                    } \r\n

                                                    if(!skipCurrentMarker) {
                                                        var latlng = [originalMarker.Latitude, originalMarker.Longitude]; \r\n

                                                        var marker = { \r\n
                                                            location: latlng, \r\n
                                                            title: originalMarker.Title \r\n
                                                        }; \r\n

                                                        if($data.model.encodeHtml) { \r\n
                                                            marker.title = DevExpress.ExpressApp.Mobile.encodeHtml(marker.title); \r\n
                                                        } \r\n

                                                        marker.onClick = function() { \r\n
                                                            var markerClickFunction = eval($data.model.markerClickFunction); \r\n                                                            
                                                            markerClickFunction(originalMarker); \r\n
                                                        }; \r\n
                                                        
                                                        var customMarkerProcessingFunctionString = $data.model.customMarkerProcessingFunction; \r\n
                                                        if(customMarkerProcessingFunctionString != undefined) { \r\n
                                                            var customMarkerProcessingFunction = eval(customMarkerProcessingFunctionString); \r\n
                                                            customMarkerProcessingFunction(mapInstance, marker, originalMarker); \r\n
                                                        } \r\n

                                                        markers.push.apply(markers, [marker]); \r\n
                                                    }
                                                })(currentMarkerIndex); \r\n                                                
                                            } \r\n

                                            mapInstance.option("markers", markers); \r\n

                                            var routesData = $data.model.routesData; \r\n
                                            if(routesData) { \r\n
                                                var useDefaultRoute = routesData.length === 1 && routesData[0].locations === undefined; \r\n
                                                if(useDefaultRoute) { \r\n
                                                    var routes = [];
                                                    if(markers.length > 1) { \r\n
                                                        var defaultRoute = $.extend({}, routesData[0]); \r\n
                                                        var locations = []; \r\n
                                                        for (var currentMarkerIndex = 0; currentMarkerIndex < markers.length; currentMarkerIndex++) { \r\n
                                                            var currentMarkerLocation = markers[currentMarkerIndex].location; \r\n
                                                            locations.push.apply(locations, [currentMarkerLocation]); \r\n
                                                        } \r\n
                                                        defaultRoute.locations = locations; \r\n
                                                        routes = [defaultRoute]; \r\n
                                                    }
                                                    mapInstance.option("routes", routes); \r\n
                                                } else { \r\n
                                                    mapInstance.option("routes", routesData); \r\n
                                                }
                                            } \r\n
                                            var customProcessDataSourceFunctionString = $data.model.customProcessDatasourceFunction; \r\n
                                            if(customProcessDataSourceFunctionString != undefined) { \r\n
                                                var customProcessDataSourceFunction = eval(customProcessDataSourceFunctionString); \r\n
                                                customProcessDataSourceFunction(mapInstance, originalMarkers); \r\n
                                            } \r\n
                                        }; \r\n
                                        dataSource.load().done(function(){ appendMarkers(); }); \r\n
                                        dataSource.on("changed", (function(){ appendMarkers(); })); \r\n
                                        
                                        var customInitializeFunctionString = $data.model.customInitializeFunction; \r\n
                                        if(customInitializeFunctionString != undefined) { \r\n
                                            var customInitializeFunction = eval(customInitializeFunctionString); \r\n
                                            customInitializeFunction(mapInstance); \r\n
                                        } \r\n
